Okweyongera okw'amangu kw'obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19) mu European Union/European Economic Area ne United Kingdom, okuva nga 1 January okutuuka nga 15 March 2020
Okujjula kw'abalwadde ba coronavirus (COVID-19) kulaga enkulaakulana efaananako bw'etyo mu mawanga ga European Union/European Economic Area ne United Kingdom ekikakasa nti, wadde nga mu kiseera kya njawulo okusinziira ku ggwanga, COVID-19 ekirwadde kyeyongedde mangu mu mawanga gonna.
Okusinziira ku byokulabirako okuva e Italy, ensi, amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'okulabirira abalwadde ab'amaanyi birina okwongera okwetegekera abantu abalina COVID-19 abajja okwetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Nga 31 December 2019, ekibinja ky'abalwadde ba pneumonia ab'ekika ekitamanyiddwa kyalagibwa mu Wuhan, mu ssaza ly'e Hubei, China.
Nga 9 Jjanwali 2020, ekitongole kya China ekirwanyisa n'okutangira endwadde kyagamba nti ekirwadde kino kiva ku kirwadde kya coronavirus ekirala kati ekiyitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obuva mu bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 buyitiddwa obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Obujulizi obuliwo bukakasa nti abantu nga 80% abalina COVID-19 balina obulwadde obutonotono, kwe kugamba, obulwadde bw'omulembe gw'omukka nga balina oba nga tebalina bulwadde bwa kkansa, era abasinga bawona.
Mu bantu nga 14%, COVID-19 yeeyongera okuba ey'amaanyi ne kiba nga kyetaagisa okujjanjabibwa mu ddwaliro ate ng'abalala 6% bafuna obulwadde obw'amaanyi obwetaagisa okujjanjabibwa ennyo.
Okufa kw'abalwadde abajjanjabirwa mu ddwaliro olw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kuli ku bitundu 4%.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, tusinziira ku mbeera y'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga lya European Union/European Economic Area (EU/EEA) ne United Kingdom (UK) era ne tubigeraageranya n'obw'essaza lya Hubei, China.
Era tugeraageranya omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK n'ogwa Italy wakati wa 31 January15 March 2020.
Abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK
Oluvannyuma lw'e China, COVID-19 yeeyongera okusaasaana mu bitundu ebirala era omuwendo gw'abantu abafa COVID-19 mu nsi yonna gukwatagana n'ogw'eggwanga lino.
Nga 11 March 2020, Dayirekita wa World Health Organization (WHO) yalangirira COVID-19 ng'ekirwadde ekirwadde.
Mu magazini ya Eurosurveillance eya Maaki 5, 2020, Spiteri et al. baategeezezza ku mulundi ogwasooka mu Bulaaya okukakasibwa nti waliwo omuntu alina COVID-19 okusinziira ku WHO.
Mu EU/EEA, abantu abasatu abaasooka okukakasibwa obulwadde baategeezebwa Bufalansa nga 24 Jjanwali 2020 mu bantu abaakomawo okuva e Wuhan, mu ssaza lya Hubei, China.
Nga 15 Maaki 2020, abantu abafunye COVID-19 baalabiddwa mu mawanga gonna 30 aga EU/EEA ne United Kingdom (UK), era wakati wa 31 December 2019 ne lunaku olwo, abantu 39,768 be bazuuliddwa nga balina obulwadde bwa COVID-19 era abantu 1,727 be baafa, nga 17,750 be bazuuliddwa nga balina obulwadde bwa COVID-19 era nga 1,441 be baafa mu Italy mwokka.
Okuzuula omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 n'obubonero bwabwe
Mu European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abalagiddwa mu buli ggwanga mu nsi yonna, oguzzibwamu okuva mu nsi ez'obuyinza nga Minisitule y'ebyobulamu, ab'obuyinza mu ggwanga n'ebitundu n'ekitongole kya WHO, guzuulibwa buli lunaku ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'oku makya.
Ebikwata ku kunoonyereza kuno byakozesebwa okussa essira ku mbeera ya COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, n'okugigeraageranya ku eyo eri mu Italy.
Ng'ekitegeeza eky'okusaasaanya kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19, twabala ennaku 14 ez'okusaasaanya kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19, nga twekenneenya engeri COVID-19 gye yeeyisaamu mu buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne Bungereza, mu kiseera kya Jjanwali 1-15 Maaki 2020.
Era twalaga omuwendo gw'abalwadde abaategeezebwa buli ggwanga nga 15 Maaki 2020 ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'oku makya nga tugeraageranya n'ogwa Italy ku 31 Jjanwali-15 Maaki 2020.
Embeera ya COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK
Embeera y'ennaku 14 ez'okuggyawo abantu abafunye COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK mu bulambalamba yagoberera eya Hubei (China) (Ekifaananyi 1).
Eri EU/EEA ne UK okutwalira awamu, obuwuka bwa COVID-19 bwatandika okweyongera nga 21 Febwali n'oluvannyuma ne bweyongera nnyo nga 28 Febwali 2020 (Eby'okuddamu).
Kino kyasinga kuva ku kwongera kw'omuwendo gw'abalwadde abavudde mu Italy, naye amawanga amalala gonna aga EU/EEA ne UK gaalaga enkulaakulana y'okweyongera kw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 (Eby'okuddamu).
Ekifaananyi 2 kiraga omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19, mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK bw'ogugeraageranya n'ogwa Italy ku 31 January-15 March 2020.
Kiraga nti, nga 15 March 8:00 a.m., amawanga amalala 15 aga EU/EEA ne UK gaali galabye dda omuwendo gw'abalwadde ogugeraageranyizibwa ku gwa Italy wiiki 3 zokka emabega oba wansi.
Ebivudde mu kunoonyereza kwaffe biraga nti omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 gweyongedde nnyo mu EU/EEA ne mu UK.
Enkulaakulana ezirabiddwa mu bungi bw'abantu abafuna COVID-19 ziraga nti ekirwadde kino kyeyongera mu maaso mu sipiidi y'emu mu mawanga gonna.
Kino wadde ng'ensi ziri mu mitendera egy'enjawulo, enjawulo mu ngeri y'okuddamu mu by'obulamu, era nga n'enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okulonda abalwadde mu nsi n'enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okulonda abalwadde abateekwa okugezesebwa okukakasa nti balina COVID-19, nga mw'otwalidde n'okugezesebwa okw'okuddamu.
Ku ntandikwa ya Maaki 2020, abasawo mu bitundu bya Italy ebyayisibwa baalaga embeera nga nga 10% ku balwadde abalina COVID-19 beetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi era emikutu gy'amawulire gyalagula nti amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi mu bitundu bino byali bituuse ku busobozi bwabyo obusingako.
Ebikwata ku kukkirizibwa kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu ddwaliro ne/oba mu kitongole ekirwadde kya maanyi kati bibaawo ku mutindo gwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6% bokka ne 1% (ebitategekeddwa).
Kyokka, byandibadde bikuŋŋaanyizibwa mu ngeri entegeke obulungi okusobola okujjuzaawo obubaka obuliwo obw'okulabirira obulina essira ku muwendo gw'abalwadde abazuuliddwa n'omuwendo gw'abafudde.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 201011 kwalaga enjawulo mu bungi bw'ebisenge eby'okujjanjaba abalwadde abali mu mbeera enzibu mu Bulaaya, okuva ku 29.2 mu Bugirimaani okutuuka ku 4.2 buli 100,000 mu Portugal.
Kino kitegeeza nti amawanga gayinza okuba n'eby'obugagga bingi oba bitono okusinga Italy (12.5 ebitanda by'abalwadde abali mu ddwaliro erikola ku bulwadde obw'amaanyi n'ebitanda by'abalwadde abali mu ddwaliro erikola ku bulwadde obw'amaanyi buli 100,000 mu 201011).
Embeera ez'okulaga ezikwata ku bujjuvu bw'obusobozi bw'obujjanjabi, n'ebiteeberezebwa ku buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne UK ku bungi bw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abajjanjabirwa mu ddwaliro nga bakwataganyizibwa n'obubenje bwa &gt; 90% obw'okusukka obusobozi bw'ebisenge eby'obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, biweereddwa mu kuddamu okw'omukaaga okw'okunoonyereza ku kabi ka ECDC ku COVID-19.
Okuva bwe kiri nti obulwadde buno bukedde mu bitundu ebimu mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, era amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'okulabirira abalwadde ab'amaanyi bitera okuweereza abantu ab'omu bitundu ebitegekeddwa obulungi, kiba kirungi okumanya ebikwata ku bulwadde n'ebisenge eby'okulabirira abalwadde ab'amaanyi ku mutindo gwa Nomenklatura y'ebifo eby'obutabanguko eby'ebyapa 2 (NUTS-2).
Okuyiga okuva mu Italy n'ebikolwa mu nsi endala biraga nti COVID-19 ekirwadde kyeyongedde mangu mu EU/EEA ne mu UK.
N'olwekyo, ensi, amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'okulabiriramu abalwadde ab'amaanyi birina okwetegekera embeera ey'okusasaanya abantu SARS-CoV-2 n'okweyongera kw'abalwadde abalina COVID-19 abeetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, nga bwe kiri mu bitundu bya Italy eby'akabi.
Nga bwe kyalagulwa mu kunoonyereza ku kabi kwa ECDC, enkola ey'amangu, ey'obutakkiriza n'ey'obutakkaanya nkulu nnyo okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kwa SARS-COV-2, nga tugenda okuva ku ngeri y'okuziyiza okutuuka ku ngeri y'okukendeeza ku bulwadde, kubanga okwongera kw'omuwendo gw'abalwadde okw'amangu okuteeberezebwa kuyinza obutatuwa abakola ensala n'amalwaliro ebiseera ebimala okutegeera, okukkiriza n'okukyusa engeri gye baddamu singa tebatandikibwawo.
Okunoonyereza ku kabi okw'amangu era kulaga enkola y'ebyobulamu bw'abantu okukendeeza ku kabi akava mu kawumpuli.
Waliwo akaseera akatono ng'amawanga galina omukisa okwongera amaanyi mu kufuga okusaasaanya SARS-CoV-2 n'okukendeeza ku kukakaalukana mu by'obulamu.
Singa kino tekikolebwa, kyangu nti enkola z'obujjanjabi mu mawanga amalala aga EU/EEA zijja kwolekagana n'okweyongera kw'abalwadde abeetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi mu nnaku ez'omu maaso oba wiiki.
Ekirwadde kya Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), ekiva ku severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kikutte abantu abasukka mu 3,000 ne kiviirako abantu abasukka mu 80,000 okufa mu China ne mu bitundu ebirala eby'ensi, ne kiviirako abantu okubonaabona.
Okufaananako akawuka kaako ak'ekika ekimu, SARS-CoV, akaaleeta SARS mu nkumi n'enkumi z'abantu mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo eyinza okusindikibwa okuva mu bambega era n'eviirako obubonero obufaanana nga bw'etyo.
Kyokka, COVID-19 erina obulwadde obutonotono n'okufa okusinga SARS naye y'esobola okusasaanya ennyo era ekosa abantu abakulu okusinga abavubuka n'abasajja okusinga abakazi.
Olw'okuba waliwo ebitabo bingi nnyo ebikwatako obulwadde buno, ekitundu kino kigezaako okuwaayo okufumiitiriza okw'enkukunala ku nsonga eno.
Tujja kwogera ku bintu ebikulu ebikwata ku bulwadde, ensibuko yabwo, obuwuka, okunoonyereza, okujjanjaba, okuteebereza, n'okutangira obulwadde.
Wadde ng'ebibuuzo bingi bikyetaaga okuddamu, tusuubira nti okunoonyereza kuno kujja kuyamba mu kutegeera n'okumalawo obulwadde buno obw'akabi.
Embaga y'Embala Eno nga January 25, 2020 efuuse ekijjukizo ekitabangawo era ekitawerabirwa eri Abakyayina bonna abaakubirizibwa okusigala awaka mu luwummula lwonna n'olw'ennaku eziwera oluvannyuma lw'okusaasaana kw'ekirwadde ekirala ekirwadde.
Akawuka kali kakwatagana nnyo ne coronavirus (CoV) eyaviirako ekirwadde kya severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) mu 2003; bwe kityo, kaayitibwa SARS-CoV-2 ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) nga February 11, 2020, era obulwadde obukwatagana nabwo bwayitibwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Ekirwadde kino kyatandika mu Wuhan, China, era ne kyanguya mu nsi yonna era ne kikwata ku bantu abalala nga 50 mu nsi yonna.
Okutuusa nga Maaki 2, 2020, akawuka kaaleeta abantu abasukka mu 80,000 abakakasibwa okuba nga balina COVID-19, nga abalwadde abasukka mu 40,000 bagobeddwa mu ddwaliro era n'abalwadde abasukka mu 3,000 baafa.
WHO erabula nti COVID-19 ye omulabe wa bantu omuwendo 1 era ayinza okuba ow'amaanyi okusinga obutujju.
Okusinziira ku PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu bbanga eritasukka myezi ebiri, ebitabo ebisukka mu 200 bifulumiziddwa ku COVID-19 omuli ne virology, epidemiology, etiology, diagnostics, n'obujjanjabi okuva ku alipoota esooka nga January 7, 2020 eyalaga enkula y'akawuka akaawera okuva mu balwadde abangi.
Okunoonyereza kuno kugezaako okuwunzika enkulaakulana mu kunoonyereza mu kitundu kino ekippya era ekikulaakulana amangu.
Buli lwe kiba kisoboka, tujja kugezaako okugeraageranya COVID-19 ne SARS n'endwadde endala eya CoV, Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS, ekyabuna mu 2012).
Era tujja kwogera ku bye tuyize okutuuka kati ku ngeri y'okutangira n'okumanya obulwadde n'ebibuuzo ebirala ebikyaliwo.
CoVs zitwalibwa okuba endwadde ezitafa eri abantu, nga ziviirako ebitundu 15% eby'ekikulukuto ekitafa.
Kyokka, mu kyasa kino, tusanze abantu abalina CoVs ez'obulwadde emirundi ebiri, kwe kugamba, SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, ezaaleetawo ekivvulu mu China mu 2003 ne Saudi Arabia mu 2012, era amangu ddala ne bisaasaana mu nsi endala nnyingi nga zirimu endwadde n'okufa eby'entiisa.
N'olwekyo, COVID-19 eyaliwo kati ye CoV eyokusatu okubalukawo mu byafaayo by'abantu.
Nga bwe kiragiddwa mu kifaananyi. Ekifaananyi.1,1, ebibinja by'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe ebitaategeerekeka byalagibwa okusooka okuva e Wuhan nga Ddesemba 31, 2019 eri akakiiko k'ebyobulamu aka China National Health Commission.
Nga wayise ennaku musanvu, enkulaakulana ya CoV yafulumizibwa.
Nga Jjanwali 15, 2020 omulwadde eyasooka okufa okuva e Wuhan yategeezebwa.
Mu kiseera ekyo, obulwadde obwo bwagenda bweyongera mu bibuga, mu ssaza, ne mu nsi eziriraanyewo.
Nga Jjanwali 20, obulwadde bwalabikidde abasawo, ekiraga nti omuntu asobola okussa obulwadde ku muntu omulala.
Nga January 23, ekibuga Wuhan kyaggalwawo nga n'entambula yaakyo yonna ey'abantu bonna emiridde.
Nga January 24, okunoonyereza okwasooka ku bulwadde kuno kwalagula nti, ku balwadde 41 abaakakasibwa, 21 bokka be baaliko akakwate n'akatale k'emmere y'ennyanja aka Wuhan akaatwalibwa okuba nti ke katandikiro k'obulwadde okuva mu nsolo etamanyi.
Nga Jjanwali 30, WHO yalangirira ekirwadde kino okuba eky'obulabe mu by'obulamu mu nsi yonna.
Mu kiseera kya alipoota eno, obulwadde buno bumaze okusaasaana mu China yonna n'ensi endala nga 50 okwetooloola ensi yonna (Ekifaananyi. (Ekifaananyi.2).2).
Olw'embeera okuba nga ekyuka mangu, omuwendo n'obuzibu bw'ekirwadde kino bikyalina okusooka okweyolesebwa.
Nga Febwali 11, 2020, okunoonyereza okw'ebifo bingi ku balwadde 8,866 omuli abalwadde 4,021 abakakasibwa COVID-19 kwalaga ekifaananyi ekikyasinzeeyo okulungamya eky'ekirwadde kino nga bwe kiragiddwa wammanga (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yakosa abantu ab'emyaka gyonna, naye okusingira ddala mu myaka 30-65.
Kumpi ekitundu (47.7%) ky'abantu abaakazuulibwa baali basukka mu myaka 50, batono nnyo abaali wansi wa 20, era abantu 14 bokka abaakazuulibwa abaali wansi w'emyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yakosa abasajja bangi (0.31/100,000) okusinga abakazi (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 yasaasaana mu bifo ebyenjawulo naddala mu Hubei ne mu bitundu ebiriraanyewo.
