Genome ya RNA eya virus efulumizibwa mu cytoplasm; oluvannyuma lw'okwekubisa genome ya virus, genomic RNA nga erina envelopu glycoproteins ne nucleocapsid proteins efulumya virion-eri mu vesicles, nga zino zifaanana ne plasma membrane okufulumya akawuka.
Enkula y'ekika kya SARS-CoV-2 eyasooka yategeezebwa nga January 10, 2020.
