SARS-CoV-2 efaanana nnyo ne SARS-CoV okusinga MERS-CoV.
Okuyitira mu kussaako obubonero bwa 'transmission electron microscopy', ebitundu bya SARS-CoV-2 byazuulibwa mu bitundu eby'obuto ennyo eby'omubiri gw'omuntu.
Abantu baasangibwa nga balina ACE2 ekikkiriza SARS-CoV-2 awamu ne SARS-CoV.
Kyokka, protein ya S eya SARS-CoV-2 ekwatagana ne ACE2 ey'omuntu mu ngeri etegudde lubege okusinga eya SARS-CoV, ekikwatagana n'ensonga nti SARS-CoV-2 evunaanyizibwa obulwadde obutono ennyo mu balwadde okusinga SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 era esobola okuzimba protein entono eya orf3b n'ensiri ya orf8.
Orf3b eya SARS-CoV-2 eyinza okuba n'ekifo mu bulwadde bw'akawuka era n'ekugira ekitangaala kya IFNβ; kyokka, orf8 terina kifo kyonna oba nsonga yonna emanyiddwa.
Nga Febwali 18, 2020, Zhou, et al., baategeezezza ku ngeri omuntu gye yali yeeyiseemu ng'ali ku ACE2 ng'alina obusobozi bwa 2,9 Å mu buzibu n'omutambuzi wa amino acid B0AT1.
Baakizuula nti ekizibu, ekyaliko enkola ez'okuzibuka n'ez'okuziikibwa, kyateekebwawo ng'ekikungo era ekizibu kya ACE2-B0AT1 kisobola okukwata obutoffaali bwa S bubiri, ekiraga nti CoV esobola okumanyibwa n'okufuna obulwadde.
B0AT1 eyinza okufuuka ekiruubirirwa eky'okujjanjaba ekirwadde ekirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2.
Ensibuko n'omulabirizi ow'omutawaana
Kimanyiddwa nti SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV byombi byava mu bululu era ne bitwalibwa ku bantu okuyita mu mbuzi ne ŋŋamira.
Okuyitira mu kugeraageranya SARS-CoV-2 n'ebirala, abalwadde b'ensiri baatwalibwa okuba omulabirizi wa SARS-CoV-2 kubanga akawuka akapya kafaanana ku bitundu 96% n'obulwadde bwa SARS obuva mu balwadde b'ensiri obuyitibwa bat-SL-CoVZX45 ne bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Kyokka, omulabirizi ki ow'omutawaana eyayamba akawuka okuyita mu kizibu ky'ebika okukwata abantu akyaali tamanyiddwa, era ekkubo ly'okusasaanya terinnaba kutegeerekeka.
Ji, et al., baalagula nti emisota gy'eyinza okuleeta akawuka okuva ku mpiso okutuuka ku bantu nga kino kizingiramu okugatta obuggya omutindo gwa S.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza, abanoonyereza mu Guangzhou, China, baalagudde nti ebinyonyi ebiyitibwa pangolins - ebirina ebinywa ebiwanvu, ebirya enku nga bitera okukozesebwa mu ddagala ly'omu China - bye bisobola okuba ebirwadde ebirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 okusinziira ku 99% ey'obutonde obufaanagana mu CoV eyazuulibwa mu pangolins ne SARS-CoV-2.
Kyokka, enjawulo ya 1% ey'ebitundu by'omubiri bibiri, era enjawulo nnene; n'olwekyo, ebivudde mu kunoonyereza kuno birindiriddwa (ekifaananyi).
Ebintu eby'omubiri n'ebya kkemikale ebya SARS-CoV-2 tebinnamanyibwa.
SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV zisobola okuwonawo mu bitoola okumala essaawa 48 mu kifo ekikalu era okutuusa ennaku 5 wansi wa 20 °C n'obusaasi bwa 40-50%.
SARS-CoV-2 eyinza okuba n'ebintu ebifaanagana.
Kyategeezeddwa nti SARS-CoV-2 ekwatibwako nnyo ebika bya ultraviolet n'ebbugumu ku 56 °C okumala eddakiika 30; etiri, 75% ethanol, eddagala eritta obuwuka eririmu klorini, peracetic acid, chloroform, n'ebirala ebirimu amasavu, naye si chlorhexidine, bisobola okuggyawo akawuka.
Abantu bonna okutwalira awamu tebalina buvunanyizibwa ku SARS-CoV-2 era bwe kityo batwalirizibwa akawuka kano.
Mu kiseera kino tewali kunoonyereza kwonna kw'obudde okwakolebwa ku ngeri omuntu gy'ayinza okuziyiza ekirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2.
N'olwekyo, tusobola okwogerako ku by'okuyiga ebyasooka ku CoV endala, naddala SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV (Fig. (Fig.4).4).
Mu bulambirira, oluvannyuma lw'akawuka okuyingira mu muntu, kusooka kutegeerwa ekitonde ky'omubiri ekirwanyisa endwadde okuyita mu biwundu ebitegeeza obuwundu obuyitibwa pattern recognition receptors (PRRs) omuli C-type lectin-like receptors, Toll-like receptor (TLR), NOD-like receptor (NLR), ne RIG-I-like receptor (RLR).
Okuyitira mu makubo ag'enjawulo, akawuka kaviirako ebirungo eby'okulumya, okukulaakulana kw'obutonde bw'obutonde, n'okusaasaanya interferons ez'ekika I (IFNs) ezikomya okusaasaana kwa kawuka era n'okwanguya okusaasaanya kwa macrophage phagocytosis ya antigen za virus.
Kyokka, protein ya N eya SARS-CoV esobola okuyamba akawuka okuva mu buwambe.
Mu bbanga ttono, obusobozi bw'omubiri obw'okwerinda obulwadde buno bukolera wamu n'okulwanyisa akawuka.
T lymphocytes omuli CD4+ ne CD8+ T cells zirina ekifo kikulu mu byokwerinda.
Obutoffaali bwa CD4+ T buleetera obutoffaali bwa B okufulumya ebirwadde ebirwanyisa akawuka, ate obutoffaali bwa CD8+ T buzikiriza butereevu obutoffaali obufunye akawuka.
T help cells zikola cytokines eziyamba ku bulwadde.
Kyokka, CoV esobola okulemesa ebikolwa bya T cell nga ereetera apoptosis ya T cells.
Obulwadde obuyitibwa humoral immunity omuli n'ebirala nga C3a ne C5a n'ebirwanyisa obulwadde buno nabyo bikulu nnyo mu kulwanyisa obulwadde bwa virus.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, antibodies ez'omulwadde eyawonyezzawo zaawangula MERS-CoV.
Ku luuyi olulala, okusaasaanya okw'amaanyi okw'obutabaako buwuka ku mubiri kuleetawo ebitundu bingi eby'ensulo ez'eddembe ebiyinza okuleetera amagumba n'ebitundu ebirala okwonooneka ennyo, ate mu mbeera embi ennyo, ebitundu bingi ne bitayinza kuwanguka oba n'okufa.
Endwadde ya SARS-CoV-2, eyogerwako ng'ey'okusaasaana mu bibiina, esobola okukosa abantu abakulu abalina obulwadde obugenda awamu n'abakazi ab'embuto.
Kyangu nnyo abantu abalina obuwuka bungi oba abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi mu mubiri okubonaabona, basinga okufuna obulwadde obwo okusinga abalala.
