Omusujja gwe gusinga okuba omubonero omukulu era ogusookera ddala ogw'akawuka ka COVID-19, nga gusobola okujjako obubonero bwonna oba obubonero obulala gamba ng'okusukkirira, okubulwa omukka, obulumi mu mibiri, okweraliikirira, obulumi bw'omutwe, obulumi mu bulago, ekisu, obulumi mu kifuba, okusaabala, okukaaba, n'okukumira.
Abalwadde abamu baafuna obwagazi n'obutafuna musaayi gwa bungi wiiki emu oluvannyuma lw'obulwadde okutandika.
Mu mbeera enzibu, abalwadde baakulaakulana mangu ne bafuna obulwadde bw'okuwummulamu obw'amaanyi, septic shock, metabolic acidosis, ne coagulopathy.
Abalwadde abalina omusujja n'obubonero bw'omu mputtu z'omukka n'omusujja ogw'amaanyi, wadde nga tebalina buzibu mu bifaananyi by'omutima, balina okwekebejjebwa akawuka okusobola okuzuula akawuka.
Okunoonyereza ku bantu mu nkomerero ya Ddesemba 2019 kwalaga nti ebitundu by'obubonero byali 98% ku bulwadde bwa ssennyiga, 76% ku kasusu ak'omukka, 55% ku dyspnea, ne 3% ku lubuto; 8% ku balwadde baali beetaaga obuyambi bw'okuyingiza empewo.
Ebizuuliddwa ebifaanana bino byalagibwa mu kunoonyereza okubiri okwakolebwa gye buvuddeko ku kibinja ky'amaka n'ekyava ku kusasaana okuva ku muntu ataalina bubonero.
Mu ngeri y'emu, okunoonyereza ku bantu mu 2012 kwalaga nti abalwadde ba MERS-CoV era baalina omusujja (98%), ekikulukuto ekikalu (47%), ne dyspnea (55%) ng'obubonero bwabwe obukulu.
Kyokka, 80% ku bo baali beetaaga obuyambi bw'okufuuyira empewo, okusinga abalwadde ba COVID-19 era nga kino kikwatagana n'obutafa bwa MERS okusinga bwa COVID-19.
Obulwadde bw'olukonvuba (26%) n'obulumi mu bulago (21%) nabyo byalabikira mu balwadde ba MERS.
Mu balwadde ba SARS, kyeyolese nti omusujja (99%-100%), okukutama (29%-75%), okussa (40%-42%), okukaaba (20-25%), n'obulumi mu bulago (13-25%) bye byali obubonero obukulu era obuyambi bw'okuyingiza empewo bwali bwetaagisa ku balwadde nga 14%-20%.
Nga Febwali 14, okufa kwa COVID-19 kwali 2%, ng'abalwadde abakakasibwa batuuse ku 66,576 mu nsi yonna.
Okugeraageranya, okufa kwa SARS mu Noovemba 2002 kwali 10% ku bantu 8,096 abaakakasibwa.
Ku MERS, okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu June 2012, okufa kwaliwo kwa 37% ku bantu 2,494 abaakakasibwa.
