Kyokka, kyalagiddwa nti abantu basobola okutwaliza awamu akawuka nga tebalina bubonero okumala wiiki ezisukka mu bbiri era n'abalwadde abawonye ne bava mu malwaliro basobola okutwaliza awamu akawuka nate, ekireetawo okweraliikirira okwongera ku kiseera eky'okusibibwa mu ddwaliro.
Abalwadde balina omuwendo gwa ssero eryeru ery'omusaayi (naddala lymphocytes) mu mbeera entandikwa nga tegukyali mutono oba nga gukoze.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, lymphopenia n'omuwendo gw'obutoffaali obweru &lt; 4×109/L omuli n'omuwendo gw'obutoffaali obweru &lt; 1×109/L, n'okuyongeza omuwendo gwa aspartate aminotransferase ne viremia byazuulibwa mu balwadde 1,099 aba COVID-19.
Emigaso gya enzyme z'ekibumba n'omusulo ne myoglobin gyayongera mu musaayi gw'abalwadde abamu, ate C-reactive protein n'ebitundu by'omusaayi ebiyitibwa erythrocytes byayongera mu musaayi gw'abalwadde abasinga.
Mu balwadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi, omuwendo gwa D- dimer, ekirungo ekikosa fibrin mu musaayi, gwali gweyongedde era omuwendo gwa lymphocyte gwali gukendeera.
Obusobyo mu bifaananyi bya radiography mu kifuba busangibwa mu balwadde ba COVID-19 abasinga era nga bulaga ebisiikirize eby'ebitundu bibiri oba ebiragala ebiriko ebiragala mu biwundu.
Abalwadde batera okufuna obulwadde bwa pulomya, obulwadde bw'amawuggwe, n'obulwadde bw'okufuna obuzibu mu mpumu.
ARDS bw'ebawo, obulwadde obwo buviirako omuntu okuzitoowererwa, amazzi okujjula, n'okufuna obulwadde bwa fibrosis.
Obunafu mu ngeri y'omusaayi gw'omu musaayi ogwa type-I n'ogw'omu musaayi ogwa type-II bukendeeza ku mutindo gwa surfactant era ne bwongera ku bbugumu eriri ku ttaka, bwe kityo ne kikendeeza ku busobozi bw'amawuggwe obw'okwongera ne kyongera ku kabi k'okuvunda.
N'olwekyo, ebizuulibwa ku bulwadde bw'omutima ebiba bizibu ennyo bifaananako n'ebyo ebiba bizibu ennyo.
Nga Febwali 18, 2020, okunoonyereza okwasooka okwa COVID-19 kwalaga nti waliwo obutoffaali bwa pneumocytes, ekisenge kya hyaline, n'obutundutundu bwa lymphocyte, n'obutoffaali bwa syncytial obuli mu biwundu by'omulwadde eyafa obulwadde buno, nga bufaanagana n'obulwadde bw'akawuka ka siriimu ne ARDS era nga bwefaanagana n'obwo obwali mu balwadde ba SARS ne MERS.
Okukebera SARS-CoV-2 RNA okuyita mu ngeri ya reverse-transcriptase polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) yakozesebwa ng'ekikopo ekikulu eky'okunoonyereza ku COVID-19.
Kyokka, olw'ebitundu ebingi eby'obulimba, ebiyinza okwongera amaanyi mu kawumpuli, obubonero bw'ekika bwatandika okukozesebwa mu kunoonyereza (obutaali bwesigamye ku RT-PCR yokka) mu China nga Febwali 13, 2020.
Embeera efaananako bw'etyo era yaliwo nga bafunye obulwadde bwa SARS.
N'olwekyo, okugatta ebyafaayo by'obulwadde, obubonero, ebigezo bya laabu, n'ebyo ebizuuliddwa mu nkola y'eby'obusannyalaze kikulu nnyo okusobola okumanya obulwadde obwo.
Nga Febwali 14, 2020, ekibiina kya Feng Zhang kyalaga enkola ey'okukozesa enkola ya CRISPR-based SHERLOCK okunoonyereza ku SARS-CoV-2, ekinoonyereza ku bitundu bya SARS-CoV-2 RNA eby'ekika ekya 20 × 10-18 mol/L okutuuka ku 200 × 10-18 mol/L (10-100 kopi buli microliter ey'eby'okuyingira) nga bikozesa dipstick mu ssaawa nga emu nga tezisigaddeyo byuma bya maanyi.
Tusuubira nti, enkola empya esobola okwongera ku buwulize n'obutebenkevu singa ekakasibwa mu bibala by'ekikyala.
Olw'obutaba na bumanyirivu ku CoV empya, abasawo basobola okusingira ddala okuwa obuyambi abalwadde ba COVID-19, nga bagezaako enkola ez'enjawulo ezaakozesebwa oba ezaali zisuubirwa eddagala lya CoV endala nga SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV n'endwadde endala ez'akawuka (Lupapula (Lupapula2).2).
Obujjanjabi buno buzingiramu obujjanjabi obuliwo n'obuliwo obuyinza okuweebwa eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka, eddagala erikendeeza ku bulwadde bw'omubiri, eddagala eriyitibwa steroids, plasma okuva mu balwadde abawonye, eddagala ly'Abayinaani, n'okuyamba mu mbeera z'obulamu.
Ne plasma okuva mu balwadde abaawonyezebwa yalagiddwa okukozesa mu bujjanjabi.
Kkampuni z'eddagala zidduka okuzimba antibodies n'eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka.
SARS-CoV-2 esingira ddala erumba amagumba ku ntandikwa era kirabika era erumba, mu kigero ekitono, ebitundu ebirala ebiraga ACE2, nga mu byenda n'ennyingo.
Wadde kiri kityo, obuzibu bw'okuwummulamu n'okulemererwa okuwummulamu bye bisinga okuleetera abalwadde okufa.
N'olwekyo, obuyambi bw'okuwummulamu bukulu nnyo okukendeeza ku bubonero n'okuwonya obulamu era buzingiramu obujjanjabi bwa oxygen obugumu, okusaasaanya ennyo omukka gwa oxygen, okufuuyira omukka, n'okufuuyira omukka okusinziira ku bunene bw'obulwadde.
Abalwadde abalina obubonero obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu balina okuzzibwamu amaanyi nga bakozesa ekirungo ekirala ekiyitibwa extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (ECMO), enkola ey'okuyingiza omutima mu mubiri ogukozesebwa mu bujjanjabi bw'obulwadde bw'omutima oba obw'okuwummulamu obuyinza okuviirako omuntu okufa.
Ng'oggyeko ekyo, okukuuma obugolokofu bw'amasannyalaze, okutangira n'okujjanjaba endwadde ez'okubiri n'okusaasaana kw'omusujja, n'okukuuma emirimu gy'ebitundu eby'omubiri ebikulu nabyo bikulu nnyo eri abalwadde ba SARS-CoV-2.
Kimanyiddwa nti omuyaga gwa cytokine guva ku kukwatibwako ekisukkiridde okw'obutabaako butawaanyizibwa mu balwadde ba SARS ne MERS.
Cytokine storm ngeri ya systemic inflammatory response ekiragibwa mu kusumululwa kwa cytokines omuli TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, ne MCP-1.
Zino cytokines zireetera obutoffaali bw'omubiri okufulumya ebitundu by'omubiri ebingi ennyo ebivaako endwadde ya ARDS n'okulemererwa kw'ebitundu by'omubiri bingi.
Okuziyiza obulwadde bw'omubiri kikulu nnyo mu bujjanjabi bw'ebizibu by'omubiri, naddala mu balwadde abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Corticosteroids ne tocilizumab, antibody ya monoclonal anti-IL6, bikozesebwa okujjanjaba cytokine storm.
Okujjanjaba okulala okw'okuziyiza obulwadde bw'omusujja gw'ensiri okuli okukyusa obuvunanyizibwa bw'obutabaako bulwadde obuggibwa ku butoffaali bwa T; okuziyiza IFN-γ, IL-1, ne TNF; okuziyiza JAK; blinatumomab; okuziyiza obubonero bw'ensiri bw'ensiri 4; n'abaziyiza HDAC.
Steroids, ng'ebirwanyisa obulwadde, zaakozesebwanga nnyo mu bujjanjabi bwa SARS okukendeeza ku buzibu bw'okusaasaana.
Kyokka, eddagala eriyitibwa steroids mu bungi teryali lya muganyulo ku bulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'amawuggwe mu balwadde ba SARS ne COVID-19.
Wabula, biyinza okuleeta obuzibu obw'amaanyi, naddala obulwadde bwa avascular osteonecrosis, ne bikola kinene ku mbeera y'omubiri.
Wadde kiri kityo, eddagala eriyitibwa corticosteroids eritali lya maanyi erisaanidde okukozesebwa mu ngeri ey'amagezi eri abalwadde ba COVID-19 abalwadde ennyo.
Mu kiseera kino eky'okuwandiika, tewali ddagala liyinza kukendeeza ku bulwadde buno.
Kyokka, okuweebwa mu musaayi ne remdesivir, ekika kya nucleotide, kyazuulibwa okuba eky'omugaso mu mulwadde wa Amerika alina COVID-19.
Remdesivir ddagala eriggya erirwanyisa akawuka eryafulumizibwa Gilead okusooka okujjanjaba endwadde eziva ku Ebola ne Marlburg.
Oluvannyuma, remdesivir era yalaga nti esobola okulemesa obuwuka obulala obuyitibwa single stranded RNA omuli MERS ne SARS.
