b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) enzyme ekwatagana n'ebitundu eby'ebweru (ebisenge by'omubiri) eby'obutoffaali mu biwundu, emisulo, omutima, ensigo, n'ebisenge.
ACE2 ekontana n'emirimu gy'ekikungo ekikyusa angiotensin (ACE) nga kikendeeza ku bungi bwa angiotensin-II n'okwongera ku Ang ((1-7) ekikikola ekirwadde ekyesigika ekirwadde kya mutima. ACE2 era ekola ng'ekifo eky'okuyingira mu butoffaali bw'obulwadde bwa coronaviruses.
Enzimu ey'omu bantu etera okuyitibwa hACE2.
Enzimu ey'okufuula angiotensin 2 y'ensimbi erimu zinc eri ku maaso ga endothelial ne mu bulala.
Protein ya ACE2 erimu ekitundu kya N-terminal peptidase M2 ne C-terminal collectrin kidney amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 ye proteini eya membrane eya type I ey'omulundi gumu, nga ensimbi yaayo ekozesa ensimbi ez'enjawulo ku bitundu by'omubiri mu biwundu ne mu bitundu ebirala.
Ekitundu kya ACE2 ekisangibwa ebweru w'omubiri kiwukanira ku kitundu kya transmembrane nga enzyme endala emanyiddwa nga sheddase, era protein esobola okuvunda evaayo n'eteekebwa mu musaayi era n'evunda.
ACE2 eri mu bitundu ebisinga: ACE2 ekwatagana ne ssensulo z'ensulo ez'ensulo ez'omu lubuto ez'ekika kya alveolar II, enterocyte ez'omubiri omutono, endothelial cells ez'omu nsalo n'ez'omu nsalo n'ensulo z'omubiri ez'omu nsalo ez'omubiri mu bitundu ebisinga.
ACE2 mRNA era esangibwa mu bwongo, mu striatum, mu hypothalamus, ne mu bwongo.
Omulimu omukulu ogwa ACE2 kwe kukola ng'omuzigo ogukontana ne ACE.
ACE esobola okugabanyaamu endowment ya angiotensin I n'ey' angiotensin II.
ACE2 nayo esobola okuggya ensimbi ya carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine okuva mu angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) n'egisobozesa okufuuka angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 era esobola okutabula peptide endala omuli [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, ne ghrelin.
ACE2 era ekakasa nti ensimbi ez'omu mubiri zigenda mu maaso ne SLC6A19 era nga kino kizingiramu obulwadde bwa Hartnup.
Ng'obutonde obuyitibwa transmembrane protein, ACE2 ekola ng'ekifo ekikulu eky'okuyingira mu butoffaali bw'obulabe bwa coronaviruses, omuli HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (akawuka akooleka SARS); ne SARS-CoV-2 (akawuka akooleka COVID-19).
Okusingira ddala, okukwatagana kwa protein ya spike S1 eya SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV2 ne enzyme ya ACE2 ku maaso g'ensulo kivaamu endocytosis n'okusenguka kwa kawuka ne enzyme mu endosomes eziri munda mu nsolo.
Enkola eno ey'okuyingira era yeetaagisa okuteekawo protein ya S ku ttooke eriyitibwa host serine protease TMPRSS2, ekikosa ekirimu okunoonyereza nga eddagala erisobola okujjanjaba. Kino kireetedde abamu okulowooza nti okukendeeza ku mutindo gwa ACE2, mu butoffaali, kiyinza okuyamba mu kulwanyisa obulwadde.
Kyokka, ebibiina by'emikono bingi n'ebitongole ebikuuma ddembe byawa amagezi okweyongera n'eddagala erikola ku bujjanjabi bw'omutonzi wa ACE ne ARB.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku lunaku lwa July 11, 2012, kwalaga nti "okukozesa eddagala erirwanyisa ACE kyaviirako abantu okukendeera ku bungi bw'obulwadde bwa pneumonia ku kigero kya 34% bw'obageraageranya n'abo abatali balwadde".
Ate era, "obubenje bw'obulwadde bwa pneumonia nabwo bwagenda bukendeera mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa eddagala erirwanyisa ACE abaalina obunafu bw'obulwadde bwa pneumonia, naddala abo abaalina obulwadde bw'omutwe n'omutima.
Okukozesa ACE inhibitors era kwaliko akakwate n'okukendeeza ku kufa okwali kukwataganyizibwa n'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe, wadde ng'ebivudde mu kunoonyereza okwo byali tebikyali bya maanyi nnyo ng'ebyo eby'obulabe bw'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe".
ACE2 (rhACE2) ey'omuntu eyazzeemu okukwatibwa ekirowoozebwa okuba obujjanjabi obupya obw'okufuna obulwadde bw'amawuggwe, era kirabika y'eyongedde okulongoosa emisulo gy'omusaayi mu mawuggwe n'okusajjulukuka kwa ssimu mu bambega abalina obulwadde bw'okubudaabuda mu mpumu obuva ku lipo polysaccharide.
RhACE2 ekwata ku bantu ekirimu ekiro kya ssaawa nga 10 era ekirimu ekirimu ekiro kya ssaawa 30 ng'oggyeko ekiseera eky'ebiseera 24 eky'obutakola.
Ebizuuliddwa bingi biraga nti rhACE2 eyinza okuba eddagala erisuubiza eri abo abatagumiikiriza enkola ya renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS inhibitors) oba endwadde ezirimu angiotensin II ey'omuwendo omungi. RhACE2 ey'okufukibwa egenda kussibwamu essira mu kukebera obulwadde bw'obutafuna bulungi mwoyo.
b'Ebikopo bya COVID-19 bye bikopo bya programu ezikozesebwa ku ssimu ezikoleddwa okuyamba mu kunoonyereza ku bantu abafunye obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe obw'omu 2019-20, kwe kugamba, enkola y'okumanya abantu ("abafunye obulwadde") abaasobola okuba nga beenyigidde mu muntu alina obulwadde.
Ebimu ku bisenge n'ebitundu by'obuyinza byaweebwa obuyambi okuva mu gavumenti.
Enkola ezitali zimu ez'okuzimba enkola z'okunoonyereza ku bantu zikoleddwa.
Okweraliikirira ku by'obuntu kuzze kweyolekera, naddala ku nkola ezisinziira ku kulabirira ebifo eby'obuntu eby'abakozesa programu.
Enkola endala ezitaali za maanyi kwe kukozesa obubonero bwa Bluetooth okuwandiika obuliraano bw'omukozesa ku ssimu endala.
Nga 10 April 2020, Google ne Apple baategeezezza nti bajja kussaawo obusobozi okuwagira programu eziri ku Bluetooth mu nkola zaabwe ez'okuweereza Android ne iOS.
Mu China, gavumenti ya China, ng'ekolagana ne Alipay, etaddewo programu esobozesa abatuuze okukebera oba nga babadde mu nkolagana n'abantu abalina COVID-19.
Kikozesebwa mu bibuga ebisukka mu 200 eby'omu China. Mu Singapore, app eyitibwa TraceTogether ekozesebwa.
App eno yateekebwawo ekibiina kya IT ekya local, yafulumizibwa nga open source era ejja kuweebwa gavumenti. North Macedonia yatandikawo "StopKorona!", app eyesigamiziddwa ku Bluetooth okukebera abantu abayinza okuba nga balina obulwadde era n'okuyamba ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu.
App eno yateekebwawo minisitule y'ebyempuliziganya n'entekinologiya ne minisitule y'ebyobulamu.
Nga 14 April 2020, app yali esembedde okukkirizibwa ku Google Play Store ne Apple App Store.
Nga 12 omwezi gwa Apuli, gavumenti yagamba nti app ey'okunoonyereza ku bantu gye yali ekola yali mu mitendera egy'okukulaakulana, era yali ejja kuba esobola okukozesebwa mu wiiki ntono. App efaananako bw'etyo etegekeddwa mu Ireland, ne mu Bufalansa ("StopCovid").
Australia ne New Zealand byombi bitunuulira enkola ezesigamiziddwa ku nkola ya TraceTogether eya Singapore ne pulaani ya BlueTrace. Russia eteekateeka okutandika enkola ey'okusiba ebifo eby'enjawulo ku balwadde abalina COVID-19 ababeera mu Moscow, nga bagendereddwa okukakasa nti tebasula waka.
Ross Anderson, profesa wa tekinologiya w'ebyokwerinda mu Cambridge University, yajuliza ebizibu bingi eby'omugaso eby'okubeera n'enteekateeka eziriko programu, omuli obulimba n'obutaba na mugaso singa abantu batono nnyo abaagala okukozesa programu.
Ng'ayogera ku kweraliikirira ku kusaasaana kw'enkola ez'obukuusa oba ez'akabi ez'obulabe bwa "coronavirus", Apple yassaawo ekkomo ku bika by'ebibiina ebiyinza okwongera ku nkola ezikwata ku coronavirus mu App Store yaayo, nga zizikugira ku bibiina byokka "eby'omu butongole" oba eby'ebitiibwa.
Google ne Amazon bitaddewo obukwakkulizo obufaanana.
Abakuuma ddembe ly'obuntu baategeezezza nti beeraliikirivu olw'ebyo ebiva mu kulondoola abantu bangi nga bakozesa programu za coronavirus, naddala ku bikwata ku ngeri ebyuma eby'okulabirira abantu ebiba byakolebwa okuziyiza ekirwadde kya coronavirus gye bijja okuggibwawo ng'akabi kagenze.
Amnesty International n'ebibiina ebirala ebisukka mu 100 byafulumya sitatimenti nga biyita okukugira okulondoola kuno.
Ebibiina byalangirira embeera munaana ku pulojekiti za gavumenti:
Okulabirira kwandibadde 'kukkirizibwa mu mateeka, kwetaagisa era nga kwa bwenkanya';
okwongera ku budde obw'okwetegereza n'okwetegereza kwandibadde n'ebiragiro eby'okulekera awo okukola;
okukozesa obubaka kwandikozeseddwa mu nsonga za COVID-19 zokka;
obukuumi bw'ebikukwatako n'obutamanyibwa kw'amannya byandibadde birina okukuumibwa era ne bikakasibwa nga bikukuumiddwa nga byesigamiziddwa ku bujulizi;
Okulabirira kwa digito kwandibadde kwewala okwongera ku busosoze n'okusibibwa ku ludda olumu;
Okugabana kwonna okw'ebikwata ku muntu omulala kwandibadde kuteekeddwa mu mateeka;
Kyandibadde kyetaagisa okuba n'obukuumi ku kukozesa obubi ebintu n'eddembe ly'abatuuze okuddamu ku kukozesa obubi ebintu;
"okwenyigira okw'omuganyulo" kw'abo bonna "abalina akakwate" kwandibadde kwetaagisa, nga mw'otwalidde n'abo abalina obumanyirivu mu by'obulamu n'ebibinja ebyawulugunyizibwa.
Enteekateeka ya Google/Apple etegekeddwa okugonjoola ekizibu ky'okwetegereza okw'enkalakkalira nga baggyamu enkola y'okunoonyereza okuva mu nkola zaabwe ez'okukozesa ebyuma byabwe nga tekikyali kyetaagisa.
Amawanga agamu gaakozesa enkola ey'okuzuula ebifo mu kifo ky'okuzuula programu, ne kiba nti kyali tekikyetaagisa kugyako kugyako okuzifuna n'okuziyiza abantu okuzizuula.
Mu Israel, okuzuula okusinziira ku mukutu kukkiriziddwa.
Enkola eziri mu mikutu egy'oku mutimbagano ezirina enkola y'okufuna obubaka bw'ekifo ekitaliiko kkomo zirina ebizibu eby'amaanyi eby'obukuumi.
Kyokka, si buli nkola erina abaweereza abakulu nti erina okufuna obubaka ku kifo omuntu gy'ali; enkola ezimu ezikuuma ebyama zaakolebwa nga zikozesa abaweereza abakulu okuwuliziganya bokka (laba akatundu akaddako).
Mu South Korea, enkola etesigamiziddwa ku programu yakozesebwa okukola okunoonyereza ku bantu be baatuusibwako.
Mu kifo ky'okukozesa app ey'enjawulo, enkola yakuŋŋaanya obubaka obw'okunoonyereza okuva mu nsibuko ez'enjawulo omuli obubaka bw'okuzuula ebyuma ebikolera ku ssimu n'obw'okukozesa kaadi, era n'ebikwataganya okufulumya obubaka okuyita mu bubaka eri abantu abayinza okuba nga balwadde.
Ng'oggyeko okukozesa obubaka buno okulabula abantu abayinza okujja gy'ali, gavumenti era ekoze obubaka bw'ekifo ekyo okutegeerekeka eri abantu bonna, ekintu ekikkirizibwa olw'enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu mateeka agakwata ku kyama ky'obuntu oluvannyuma lw'obulwadde bwa MERS mu ggwanga eryo.
Amagezi gano gali ku bantu bonna okuyita mu programu ezitali zimu ne ku mukutu gwa Intaneeti.
Nga 6 April 2020, eby'okuddamu tebinnateekebwa mu bujjuvu.
Okukebera omuntu yenna okukuuma ebyama bye kyekimu ku bintu ebimanyiddwa ennyo, nga waliwo ebitabo bingi eby'okunoonyereza okuva mu 2013.Ku 7 Apuli 2020, ebibinja by'abakugu ebisukka mu kkumi na bibiri byali bikolera ku ngeri y'okukuuma ebyama, gamba ng'okukozesa Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) okuwandiika obusemberero bw'omukozesa ku ssimu endala.
Kyokka, PEPP-PT y'enteekateeka y'okukwataganya ebikwatagana n'obukulembeze n'obutongole, era si nkola emu.Enkola ez'obukulembeze ez'obukulembeze ez'obukulembeze zirimu Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact Numbers (TCN, fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN), Privacy Sensitive Protocols and Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT) n'endala.
Mu nkola zino, obubaka obw'obuntu obumanyibwa tebuva ku kyuma, era okukwatagana kwonna kubaawo ku kyuma.
Ekibinja ky'obukuumi ku MIT Media Lab kibadde kikola ku SafePaths, ekitebe eky'okukozesa enkola ez'okukuuma obukuumi nga kikuŋŋaanya era nga kikozesa obubaka bw'ekifo oba ekkubo ery'okusala ekkubo okukwata ku kusaasaana kwa COVID-19.
Kisinziira ku kunoonyereza okuva mu whitepaper "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" eyafulumizibwa mu March 2020.Ekintu ekirala ekikwatagana nakyo ye SafeTrace platform eya Enigma MPC, kkampuni ekola ku tekinologiya w'obukuumi era nga nayo yatandikibwawo ku MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ekozesa tekinologiya wa hardware omutebenkevu okusobozesa abakozesa okugabana obubaka obw'obutebenkevu n'obw'obulamu n'abakozesa abalala n'abakungu, nga tebasse mu bukuumi bwa bubaka obwo.
Nga 5 Apuli 2020, ekibiina kya TCN Coalition kyateekebwawo ebibiina ebyali bigabanyizza awamu ku ngeri y'emu era nga mu bungi birina enkola ezikwekwetoolodde, nga kirina ekigendererwa eky'okukendeeza ku kusattulukuka, n'okusobozesa okussa ekimu kw'ensi yonna kw'okuzuula n'okulangirira programu, ekintu ekikulu mu kutuuka ku kukkiriza okwabaddewo.
Nga 9 April 2020, gavumenti ya Singapore yalangirira nti yali yafulumya enkola ya BlueTrace ekozesebwa mu nkola ya gavumenti.
Nga 10 April 2020, Google ne Apple, amakampuni agafuga emikutu gya Android ne iOS, gaalangirira enteekateeka ey'okunoonyereza ku mikwano gyabwe, gye baagambye nti ejja kukuuma obukuumi, nga bwesigamye ku kukozesa tekinologiya wa Bluetooth Low Energy n'okuwandiika ebigambo ebikuuma obukuumi.
Era baafulumya n'obutegeeza ku tekinologiya omukulu akozesebwa mu nkola eno.
Okusinziira ku Apple ne Google, enkola eno eteekeddwa okutandikibwawo mu mitendera esatu:
okutandikawo ebyuma ebireetera gavumenti okukola enkola ez'okunoonyereza ku coronavirus ezikuuma ebyama
okugatta obusobozi buno butereevu mu iOS ne AndroidGoogle ne Apple bateekateeka okugonjoola ebizibu by'okwetegereza n'okwetegereza okw'okweyongerawo nga basooka kugabira enkola nga bayita mu kukyusa enkola y'okukola, era oluvannyuma ne bagiggyawo mu ngeri y'emu ng'akabi kagenze.
b'Okuteeka eddagala mu kifo ekirala (era ekimanyiddwa nga okuteeka eddagala mu kifo ekirala, okuteeka eddagala mu mbeera endala, okuteeka eddagala mu kifo ekirala oba okukyusa eddagala) kwe kutereka eddagala erikkirizibwa okujjanjaba obulwadde oba embeera y'ekisawo eyawukana ku eyo gye lyakolebwa.
Kino kye kimu ku byobuvunanyizibwa mu kunoonyereza ku bya sayansi nga kati kikoleddwa okukulaakulanya obujjanjabi obumatiza n'obutuukiriza obulungi obwa COVID-19.
Enkola endala ez'okunoonyereza zirimu okutandikawo eddagala erigema COVID-19 n'okuteekebwamu plasma. SARS-CoV-2 erina obutoffaali nga 66 obuyinza okujjanjabibwa, nga buli emu erina ebifo bingi eby'okuteekawo enkola.
Okunoonyereza ku bifo ebyo eby'okusiba kiwa pulojekiti ey'okuzimba eddagala erigema akawuka ka COVID-19 erigema obutoffaali.
Ku bupolyetini obusinga obukulu SARS-CoV-2 bw'esobola okukozesa kwe papayin-like protease, RNA dependent RNA polymerase, helicase, S protein, ne ADP ribophosphatase.
Hussein A, et al yasoma ebika by'eddagala ebiwerako eby'enjawulo oluvannyuma ne bizuulibwa era ne bijjukirwa olw'okufaanagana kwabyo n'eddagala erisingayo okuba ery'omugaso erikkirizibwa okusobola okwanguya enkulaakulana y'eddagala erirwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 mu kunoonyereza kwe okwaliwo nga tannasalawo kulabulwa mu kunoonyereza.
Chloroquine ddagala erirwanyisa omusujja gw'ensiri era ekozesebwa n'okulwanyisa endwadde ezimu ez'obutafa.
Nga 18 March, WHO yalangirira nti chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine eyagikuŋŋanako byali biri mu ddagala ennya eryali lisomebwa ng'ekitundu ky'okugezesebwa kw'ekikyenyetso.
Gavana wa New York Andrew Cuomo yalangirira nti okugezesebwa kwa chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine mu New York State kwandibadde kutandika nga 24 March. Nga 28 March, FDA yakkiriza okukozesa hydroxychloroquine sulfate ne chloroquine phosphate wansi w'Ekiragiro ky'Okukoleramu mu Bbanga Lyonna (EUA).
Obujjanjabi tebukkiriziddwa mu nkola y'okugezesebwa kwa kliniki kwa FDA era bukkiriziddwa wansi wa EUA nga bujjanjabi bw'okugezesa bwokka obw'okukozesa mu bwangu mu balwadde abali mu ddwaliro naye nga tebasobola kufuna bujjanjabi mu kukeberwa kwa kliniki.
CDC egamba nti "okukozesa, eddagala, oba ebbanga ly'omwenge gwa hydroxychloroquine olw'okutangira oba okujjanjaba obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2" tekinnategeerekeka.
Abasawo bagamba nti bakozesa eddagala lino "bwe baba nga tebalina kya kwekolera".
Ekibinja ky'abanoonyereza eky'omu Turkey mu Istanbul kikoze okunoonyereza okutono ku kukozesa chloroquine nga ekozesebwa awamu ne zinc, vitamin A, vitamin C ne vitamin D.
Okunoonyereza okw'amaanyi kugenda mu maaso ku ssomero lya Duke University ne ssomero lya Oxford.
NYU Langone Medical School ekola okugezesebwa ku bukuumi n'obwanguzi bw'okukozesa hydroxychloroquine.
Okugezesebwa kw'omu China mu Wuhan ne Shenzhen kwagamba nti favipiravir yali "nnyangu nnyo".
