Mu abo abakoseddwa ennyo, COVID-19 esobola okukulaakulana mangu ne yeeyisa ng'omulwadde ow'obutafuna bulungi mwoyo (ARDS) ekiviirako okulemererwa okuwummulamu, septic shock oba obulemererwa kw'ebitundu by'omubiri bingi.
