Kyokka, abalwadde abaatwalibwa mu ICU baalina ekiseera kya nnaku musanvu wakati w'okusibibwa mu ddwaliro n'okufa.
Mu kunoonyereza ku balwadde abaasooka, ekiseera ekituufu okuva ku kulaga obubonero obwasooka okutuuka ku kufa kyali ennaku 14, nga buli lunaku luweza ennaku mukaaga okutuuka ku 41.
Mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa National Health Commission (NHC) eya China, abasajja baalina omuwendo gw'abafu ogwa 2.8% ate abakazi baalina omuwendo gw'abafu ogwa 1.7%.
Okunoonyereza ku biwuka eby'omu musaayi okuva mu biwundu byalagula obuvune mu biwundu byombi.
Enkyukakyuka z'ekika kya virus mu biwuka byalagibwa mu pulomosiiti.
Ekifaananyi ky'omubba kyali kifaanana eky'obulwadde bw'okufuba okubudaabuda omubiri (ARDS).
Mu 11.8% ku kufa okwategeezebwa National Health Commission of China, obulwadde bw'omutima bwalabikira olw'obunene bwa troponin oba okuyimirira kw'omutima.
Okusinziira ku biwandiiko okuva mu March okuva mu Amerika, 89% ku abo abajjanjabirwa mu ddwaliro baalina obulwadde obwali bubeewo. Okubeerawo kw'ebikozesebwa eby'ekisawo n'embeera y'eby'enfuna mu kitundu nakyo kiyinza okukwata ku kufa.
Okubala okufa okuva mu mbeera eno kwawukana olw'enjawulo ezo ez'ebitundu, naye era olw'ebizibu by'enkola.
Okuba nti abantu abafa obulwadde buno si bangi kiyinza okuviirako abantu okufa ennyo.
Kyokka, ekituufu nti okufa kuva mu balwadde abaakafuna obulwadde buno mu biseera ebyayita kiyinza okutegeeza nti omuwendo gw'abafa mu kiseera kino tegukwatagana bulungi.
Abanywa ssigala baali emirundi 1.4 okusingawo okuba n'obubonero obw'amaanyi obw'akawuka ka COVID-19 era nga emirundi nga 2.4 okusingawo okuba nga beetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi oba okufa bw'obageraageranya n'abatali banywi ba ssigala. Okweraliikirira kweyongedde ku bikwata ku biva mu bulwadde buno.
Ekitongole ky'Eddwaliro lya Hong Kong kyazuula nti abantu abamu abaawona obulwadde buno, ebitundu byabwe byavaako ebitundu 20 okutuuka ku 30 ku buli kikumi.
Kino era kiyinza okuviirako obulwadde obuyitibwa post-intensive care syndrome oluvannyuma lw'okuwona.
Okutuusa mu Maaki 2020, tekimanyiddwa oba obulwadde obwayitamu mu biseera ebyayita buwa obutebenkevu obumala mu bantu abawona obulwadde.
Obulwadde buno buyinza okuzuulibwa, okusinziira ku nneeyisa ya koronavairusi endala, naye waliwo abantu abazuuliddwa oluvannyuma lw'okuwona COVID-19 ne bafuna obujanjabi bwa koronavairusi.
Embeera zino zikkirizibwa okuba okwonooneka kw'obulwadde obumaze ebbanga nga bubeerawo mu kifo ky'okufuna obulwadde obuzzeemu.
Obuwuka buno bwekikkirizibwa okuba obw'obutonde era nga buva mu nsolo, okuyita mu bulwadde obuyitiridde.
Ensibuko yennyini temanyiddwa, naye mu Ddesemba 2019 okusaasaana kw'obulwadde bwali kumpi buva ku kusasaana okuva ku muntu okudda ku muntu.
Okunoonyereza ku bantu 41 abaasooka okukakasibwa COVID-19, okwakubibwa mu January 2020 mu The Lancet, kwalaga olunaku olusembayo olw'okwoleka obubonero nga 1 December 2019.
Ebitabo bya WHO byalagula nti obulwadde bwatandika okweyoleka nga 8 December 2019.
Ebiragiro bingi bitera okukozesebwa okubalirira okufa.
Ennamba zino zikyuka okusinziira ku bitundu n'ebiseera era zisinziira ku bungi bw'okugezesebwa, engeri y'enteekateeka y'obujjanjabi, enkola y'obujjanjabi, ekiseera okuva ku kutandika kw'obulwadde n'ebiri mu bantu gamba ng'emyaka, ekikula n'obulamu bwonna.
Mu nkomerero ya 2019, WHO yawa ICD-10 obulwadde obw'amangu obuyitibwa U07.1 ku kufa okuva ku bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 obwasimbiddwa mu laboratory ne U07.2 ku kufa okuva ku COVID-19 eyazuulibwa mu ddwaaliro oba mu bulwadde bw'abantu nga tewali bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 obwasimbiddwa mu laboratory. Enjawulo y'okufa n'obulwadde eraga omuwendo gw'abantu abafudde nga bagobeddwa omuwendo gw'abalwadde abazuuliddwa mu kiseera ekimu.
Okusinziira ku byenkanyizo bya Yunivasite ya Johns Hopkins, omuwendo gw'abantu abafa ku buli mulwadde mu nsi yonna gwa 6.9% (153,822/2,240,191) nga 17 Apuli 2020.
Omuwendo gwawo gukyuka okusinziira ku kitundu.Ebintu ebirala omuli omuwendo gw'abantu abafa (CFR), ekiraga ebitundu by'abantu abafa obulwadde, n'omuwendo gw'abantu abafa obulwadde (IFR), ekiraga ebitundu by'abantu abafa obulwadde (abazuuliddwa n'abatazuuliddwa) abafa obulwadde.
Ebiwandiiko bino tebirina kiseera kye bimala era bigoberera abantu ab'enjawulo okuva ku bulwadde okutuuka ku kugonjoola obulwadde.
Wadde ng'abantu bonna abalina akawuka tebafuna bulwadde buno, obuwuka obwo bwe bubawo buyinza okuyamba okumanya abantu bameka abafunye akawuka kano.
Mu kifo ekikulu eky'ekirwadde kino mu Italy, Castiglione d'Adda, ekyalo ekitono ekirimu abantu 4600, 80 (1.7%) bafudde dda.
Mu Gangelt, obulwadde bwabuna olw'embaga z'embaga, era ne busaasaana n'eri abantu abato, ne kiviirako okufa okutono, era si bonna abafa COVID-19 nti bayinza okuba nga baakulembeddwamu mu butongole.
Ate era, embeera y'ebyobulamu mu Bugirimaani teyeeyongedde.
Mu Netherlands, abantu nga 3% bayinza okuba n'ebirwanyisa, okusinziira ku abo abawaddeyo omusaayi.
69 (0.004% ku bantu) bakakasibwa okufa COVID-19.
Obuzibu bw'ekirwadde kino n'omuwendo gw'abafa gwa njawulo ku basajja n'abakazi.
Okufa kusingawo mu basajja mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu China ne Italy.
Abasajja be basinga okuteeberezebwa okuba n'obubenje mu myaka gyabwe 50, ng'obutali bumu wakati w'abasajja n'abakazi busembayo ku myaka 90.
Mu China, abasajja bafa ebitundu 2.8 ku buli kikumi ate abakazi bafa ebitundu 1.7 ku buli kikumi.
Ensonga ez'enkukunala ezireetera abantu okweyawula ku basajja n'abakazi tezimanyiddwa, naye ebintu eby'ekika n'enneeyisa biyinza okuba nga bye biviirako.
Enjawulo mu by'omubiri eziri mu kwegatta, okunywa ssigala mu bakyala n'abasajja abatalina bulwadde nga pulogulaamu y'omusaayi ng'omusaayi okuwera mu myaka gy'obuto okusinga abakyala, biyinza okuba nga byaviirako okufa kw'abasajja okuwera.
Mu Bulaaya, 57% ku bantu abafunye obulwadde baali basajja ate 72% ku abo abaafa COVID-19 baali basajja.
Okutuusa mu Apuli 2020, gavumenti ya Amerika teriiko bujulizi bwensi obukwata ku bulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Okunoonyereza kulaga nti endwadde ez'obulabe nga Ebola, HIV, ekikulukuto ne SARS zikwata ku basajja n'abakazi mu ngeri ez'enjawulo.
Ebitundu ebisingako ku bakozi b'ebyobulamu, naddala abasawo, bakazi, era balina omukisa omungi ogw'okufuna akawuka.
Ekitongole ky'Eby'obulamu eky'Ensi Yonna kyalangirira nga 11 Febwali 2020 nti erinnya ly'ekirwadde erya bulijjo lya kuba "COVID-19".
Akulira WHO Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yannyonnyodde nti CO ekiikirira corona, VI ekiikirira akawuka, D ekiikirira obulwadde, ate 19 kitegeeza lwe kyazuulibwa omulundi ogwasooka: 31 December 2019.
Erinnya lino lyalondebwa okwewala okwogerako ku kifo ekimu (ng'ekyokulabirako, China), ebika by'ebisolo oba ebibinja by'abantu, okusinziira ku magezi g'ensi yonna ag'okuyita amannya agagendereddwa okwewala okuvumibwa. Akawuka akooleka COVID-19 kayitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
WHO era ekozesa "akawuka ka COVID-19" ne "akawuka akakola ku COVID-19" mu kubuulira.
Obulwadde n'akawuka byombi biyitibwa "coronavirus".
Mu kiseera eky'okusaasaana okwasooka mu Wuhan, China, akawuka n'obulwadde byayitibwanga "coronavirus" ne "Wuhan coronavirus".
Mu Jjanwali 2020, WHO yasalawo 2019-nCov ne 2019-nCoV obulwadde obw'omu bwongo obw'amaanyi ng'amannya ag'ekiseera ag'akawuka n'obulwadde okusinziira ku bulagirizi bwa 2015 obukwata ku kukozesa ebifo mu mannya g'obulwadde n'akawuka.
Amannya g'ekikugu COVID-19 ne SARS-CoV-2 gaafulumizibwa nga 11 February 2020.
Olw'obutaba na busobozi mu bizinensi ez'obujjanjabi, abazimbi abamu aba digito baakuba ebikozesebwa mu by'obujjanjabi nga ebikozesebwa mu nnyindo n'ebitundu by'ebyuma ebikuuma omukka.
Mu kyokulabirako ekimu, eddwaliro ly'e Italy bwe lyali lyetaaga nnyo vvulpi ya ventilator, era omuteresi yali tasobola kugiwa mu budde obwetaagisa, ekitongole ekimu ekyaggulawo amaduuka kyabaako ne ky'ekikolera era ne kifulumya vvulpi 100 ezaali zeetaagisa ekiro.
Oluvannyuma lw'okusaasaana kwa COVID-19, endowooza z'obukumpanya, obubaka obutali butuufu n'obubbi byajjawo ku nsibuko, omuwendo, okutangira, okujjanjaba n'ebintu ebirala eby'obulwadde era ne bisaasaana mangu ku mutimbagano.
Abantu kirabika basobola okusaasaanya akawuka ku nsolo endala.
Okunoonyereza tekwazuula bujulizi bwa virus okuzaala mu mbizzi, ebinazi, n'enkoko.
Tewali ddagala oba bulwadde bwonna obukkirizibwa okujjanjaba obulwadde buno.
Okunoonyereza okw'ensi yonna ku ddagala n'eddagala ku COVID-19 kugenda mu maaso n'ebitongole bya gavumenti, ebibiina by'abasomi n'abanoonyereza mu makolero.
Mu March, Ekitongole ky'Eby'obulamu eky'Ensi Yonna kyatandikawo "Okukebera kw'Obuwulize" okukebera ebikolwa by'obujjanjabi bw'eddagala erina obuwuka obutta akawuka nga lirina obusobozi obusingawo.
Tewali ddagala liyinza kukozesebwa, naye ebitongole eby'enjawulo bikolera ku ddagala erigenda okuteekebwamu.
Omulimu ogwakolebwa edda ku SARS-CoV gugenda kukozesebwa kubanga SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikozesa ACE2 receptor okuyingira mu butoffaali bw'omuntu.
Waliwo enkola ssatu ez'okulwanyisa endwadde ezinoonyerezebwako.
Okusooka, abanoonyereza baagala okuzimba eddagala erigema akawuka.
Okukozesa akawuka ng'ako, ka kube nga tekakola oba nga kafiiriddwa, kigendererwa kya kuleetawo okwanukula okw'amangu okw'omubiri gw'omuntu eri obulwadde obuggya obw'ekikukkulaakulana ekya COVID-19.
Enkola ey'okubiri, eddagala erikola ku busawo, erina ekigendererwa eky'okuteekawo eddagala erireetera obuwuka obw'omubiri okuwulira obusimu obw'omubiri ku busawo obumu obw'akawuka.
Ku nsonga ya SARS-CoV-2, okunoonyereza ng'okwo kwesigamye ku protein ya S-spike eyamba akawuka okuyingira mu ACE2 enzyme receptor.
Enkola eyokusatu y'ey'okulwanyisa ekirwadde kya nucleic acid (okusiiga eddagala lya DNA oba RNA, enkola empya ey'okuteekawo eddagala).
Enjaga ez'okugezesa okuva mu emu ku nkola zino zandibadde zikeberebwa okulaba oba nga nnungi era nga zirimu emiganyulo. Nga 16 March 2020, okugezesebwa okwasooka okw'ekikopo kw'ekirwadde kwatandika n'abakkiriza bana mu Seattle.
Ekirwadde kino kirimu code y'ekika ekitaliiko kabi ekikoppebwa okuva mu kawuka akooleka obulwadde. Okuteekawo ebirwadde ebiva ku antibody kyayogerwako ng'okusoomooza okuyinza okubaawo mu kutandikawo eddagala erigema ekirwadde kya SARS-COV-2, naye kino kyawukanako.
Waliwo okugezesebwa kwa kliniki okusukka mu 300 okwaliwo mu April 2020.
Okugezesebwa musanvu kwali kukebera obujjanjabi obwakkirizibwa dda ku bulwadde bwa siriimu, omuli okunoonyereza kwa mirundi ena ku hydroxychloroquine oba chloroquine.
Eddagala erigema akawuka eriddamu okukola ku nsonga z'abantu abasinga obungi mu kunoonyereza okw'omu China, nga waliwo okunoonyereza kw'ekitundu eky'okusatu ku remdesivir mu nsi eziwerako okujja okukoleddwa ku nkomerero ya Apuli.
Okutandika ne Apuli 2020, waaliwo okwekebera okw'amaanyi ku nkulaakulana y'eddagala erigendereddwa ku ddagala lya COVID-19 ne eddagala. Eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka erimu libalibwa ku bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19, omuli remdesivir, chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir ne lopinavir/ritonavir nga zizannyiddwaako ne interferon beta.
Waliwo obujulizi obusooka obw'obuyambi bwa remdesivir, okuva mu Maaki 2020.
Obulwadde bwagenda bulungi mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa remdesivir ey'ekisa.
Okugezesebwa kw'ekibinja III kukolebwa mu Amerika, China ne Italy. Chloroquine, eyakozesebwanga eddagala lya malaria, yasomebwa mu China mu Febwali 2020, n'ebivudde mu kusooka.
Kyokka, waliwo abasaba okunoonyereza kuno okulambulwe.
Ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu mu Korea ne China basabye okukozesa kloroquine.
Kyokka, ekitongole kya Wuhan Institute of Virology, wadde nga kiwa amagezi ku ddagala erimu erya buli lunaku, kigamba nti emirundi ebiri eddagala eryo lya kabi nnyo era liyinza okutta.
Nga 28 Maaki 2020, FDA yafulumya olukusa olw'okukozesa mu bwangu hydroxychloroquine ne chloroquine okusinziira ku magezi g'abasawo abajjanjaba abantu abalina COVID-19. Amateeka g'omu China agafulumizibwa mu nnamba 7 era gazingiramu interferon, ribavirin oba umifenovir okukozesebwa ku COVID-19.
Ebyafaayo biraga nti eddagala eriyitibwa ribavirin eringi lyetaagisa okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu vitro.
Nitazoxanide asaliddwa mu kunoonyereza mu vivo oluvannyuma lw'okulaga obuzibu bw'okukugira SARS-CoV-2. Okunoonyereza kulaga nti okusooka okuteeka mu nkola protein ey'ekika ekya protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) kikulu nnyo eri okuyingira kwa SARS-CoV-2 okuyita mu kukwatagana ne ACE2.
Okunoonyereza ku chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine nga n'azithromycin oba nedda, birina obunafu obw'amaanyi obulemesa abasawo okukozesa enzijanjaba zino nga tebannanoonyereza. Oseltamivir teziziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu vitro era terina buvunaanyizibwa mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19.
Omusulo gwa cytokine guyinza okuba ekizibu mu mitendera egy'oluvannyuma egy'ekikambwe ekya COVID-19.
Waliwo obujulizi obulaga nti hydroxychloroquine esobola okuba n'ebika eby'okulwanyisa sitokini. Tocilizumab yatwalibwa mu bulagirizi bw'obujjanjabi ne National Health Commission ya China oluvannyuma lw'okufundikira okunoonyereza okutono.
Kyeyongera okugezesebwa mu kitundu kya 2 ku mutindo gw'eggwanga mu Italy oluvannyuma lw'okulaga ebivudde mu bantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Nga kikwataganyizibwa n'okugezesebwa kw'omusaayi gwa serum ferritin okumanya ebirombe bya cytokine, kigendereddwa okuziyiza enkulaakulana ng'ezo, eziteeberezebwa okuba ensibuko y'okufa mu bantu abamu abakoseddwa.
Ekirwanyisa ekikwatagana n'ebikwatagana ne interleukin-6 kyaweebwa olukusa lwa FDA okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku bujjanjabi bw'obulwadde bwa steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome obuva ku nsonga endala, CAR T cell therapy, mu 2017.
Okutuusa kati, tewali bukakafu bwonna bulaga nti tocilizumab ya mugaso mu kujjanjaba CRS.
Okuyingiza antibodies ez'omubiri ez'abo abawonye COVID-19 mu bantu abazeetaaga, nga zino ze zikola ku by'omubiri, ez'omubiri ogutafa, ezinoonyerezaako ng'enkola ey'okwerinda.
Enkola eno yagezesebwa ku SARS nga teriiwo bibala.
Okuggyawo akawuka y'engeri y'okukikolamu ekisuubirwa nti eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka erisobola okuyambako mu kulwanyisa SARS-CoV-2.
Kyokka, enkola endala, gamba nga cytotoxicity ey'omu nsusso ezirimu ebitundu by'omubiri ebiwakanya omubiri n'okusaasaanya ekirungo (phagocytosis) zisobola okubaawo.
Engeri endala ez'okujjanjaba n'omubiri ogumu, gamba ng'okukozesa omubiri ogumu ogukozesebwa mu kutema emizannyo, zikyali mu kutandikibwawo.
Okweyongerayongera kw'omusaayi ogukomawo, oguzingiramu omuwendo gw'omusaayi oguli mu musaayi gw'abalwadde abawonye era oguliko ebirwanyisa obulwadde buno, kiyinza okwongera ku bangu bw'okukozesa.
